data.title: The gulls with rings wintering in Basel, Switzerland
data.text:
The gulls with rings wintering in Basel

Basel; place ringed; place observed; Click the marker to see the ring code

Belarus (White Russia)

K313 seen on the Rhine at the Dreilaendereck, ringed in June 2020 in Minsk

Croatia

S8E3 observed 9. Jan 2015 and 3. Jan. 2016 in Park im Gruenen in Muenchenstein was ringed in Dec. 2013 as one-year bird in Jakusevec in Central Croatia.

SP6K - observed 22. Dec. 2017 and also 17. Nov. 2018 in Birsfelden was ringed in Jakusevec near Zagreb in Feb. 2017.

S2BY observed 13. Jan 2019 on Rhine by Dreilaenderbruecke, Weil am Rhein, was ringed in Jakusevec in Central Croatia in dex. 2016.

Czechia

ET10.212 N.MUSEUM PRAHA observed 11. Jan. 2018 on Rhine in Basel and also next winter 31.12.2018 in Park im Gruenen in Muenchenstein was ringed as pullus in June 2016 in Ceska Skalice, Czech Republic.

Z84J observed 20. Nov. 2018 on Rhine in Basel was ringed in May 2018 as an adult bird in Ceska Skalice

EX77188 PRAHA observed 30. Dec. 2018 on Rhine in Basel

Denmark

V94R einged in December 2020 in Odense, observed in Dexember 2021 in Muenchenstein at the Gruen 80 lakes

Estonia

ESTONIA-MATSALU U-501802 observed 4. Jan. 2019 on Rhine in Weil am Rhein, ringed Jun 2017 as pullus in Toestamaa at the Baltic Sea shore.

Finland

HELSINKI ST296385 observed 13. Jan. 2019 in Kleinhueningen, ringed 23. 6. 2013 in Outokompu 2150 km from Basel!

Germany

XC42 HIDDENSEE IA 086 273 - observed 1. Jan. 2017 on Rhine canal in Village-Neuf (FR) was ringed in Dec. 2012 in Blasewitz near Dresden.

XC42 HIDDENSEE IA 086 273 - three years later the bird is again here, observer 18. Jan. 2020 at the same place. Who knows what it did and where it was during these 3 years?

AF069 observed 31. Dec. 2017 on Rhine in Dreilaendereck and 9. Dec. 2018 in Kleinhueningen (2nd wintering here) was ringed in Nov. 2016 in Hamburg.

Hungary

HMLK This bird with red plastic ring was observed 17. Jan. 2020 at Kleinhueningen, was ringed in February 2018 in Budapest.

Lithuania

HA-45507 KAUNAS, LITHUANIA - observed 9. Dec. 2018 on river Wiese in Kleinhueningen (part of Basel) was ringed in June 2018 as nestling in eastern Lithuania - 1531 km from Basel!

Netherlands

ERJ1 ARNHEM, HOLLAND - observed 11. Jan. and 1. Feb. 2018 on Rhine in Basel was ringed as young bird in Aug. 2016 in Arnhem.

Poland

T974 observed 11. Jan. 2018 on Rhine in Basel, was ringed in May 2015 as adult bird in Januszkowice; this bird carries also the web adress where to report the obervation with it!

65.328 ORN GDANSK POLAND observed 31. Jan 2016 Park im Gruenen in Muenchenstein

T4XR observed 15. Feb 2016 in Park im Gruenen in Muenchenstein

TYHE observed 20. Nov. 2018 on Rhine in Village-Neuf (FR), was ringed in June 2018 in Turek, Central Poland as an adult bird.

T2R4 POLAND - observed 31. Jan. 2016 on Rhine in Village-Neuf (FR).

T927 observed 20. Jan 2018 on Rhine in Basel was ringed in May 2015 as pullus in Januszkowice, this bird was observed also in Sempach (CH) and Utrecht (NNL).

T6HC - observed 22. Dec. 2017 and also in 17. Nov. 2018 in Birsfelden, ringed in May 2017 as adult bird in Mietkow.

FN90.574 GDANSK POLAND - observed 15. Feb. 2016 in Park im Gruenen in Muenchenstein.

Russia

PS22707 MOSKVA - observed 30. Dec. 2018 in Park im Gruenen in Muenchenstein, ringed on lake Ilmen, near Veliky Novgorod (1989 km from Basel), on 1.6.2016 as pullus.

Slovakia

H22893 N.MUSEUM BRATISLAVA - observed 2. Jan. 2018 in Park im Gruenen in Muenchenstein, the bird was ringed in June 2017 as pullus in Piestany.

Sweden

6429705 STOCKOLM observed 25. Dec. 2019 on Rhine in Basel, ringed in March 2009 as adult bird in Malm√∂.

Switzerland

K80271 VOGELWARTE SEMPACH - observed 2. Feb. 2019 on Rhine in Village Neuf (FR), was ringed as adult bird in March 2007 at Sempachersee (CH). The bird is therefore at least 14 years old (one can see this also from the look of the ring). This gull is quite a traveller, in the meantime it was reported from central Poland and from Friedrichshafen in Germany.

K118821 VOGELWARTE SEMPACH - observed 2. Jan. and 10. Feb. 2018 in Park im Gruenen in Muenchenstein and also next winter on 26. Dec. 2018 at the same place, was ringed as young bird in December 2017 in Oberkirch (Luzern).

K118694 VOGELWARTE SEMPACH - observed 30. Nov. on Rhine in Basel, was ringed in October 2016 as adult bird in Oberkirch on Sempachersee.

K87261 VOGELWARTE SEMPACH - observed 19. Feb. 2016 in Huningue

Ukraine

U775 - observed 27. Dec. 2018 on Rhine in Village-Neuf (FR), was ringed in June 2018 as a chick in central Ukraine, 1410 km distant

In January 2020 the bird is wintering in the same place.

Caspian Gull

X899 - observed 22. Dec. 2017 on Rhine in Birsfelden. The bird was ringed in May 2017 as pullus on Graebendorfer See in Germany.
